data.description: Welcome to your new home! This charming 3-bedroom, 2.5-bath traditional style residence in the Westbrook community offers a host of modern upgrades, including a 65" TV in the living room and a 75" TV in the fully finished walk-out basement. The main level features real hardwood floors, a brick wood-burning fireplace, and an updated kitchen with a pantry. Upstairs, find two secondary bedrooms, an updated full bathroom, and a spacious bonus room over the garage. The primary suite boasts a large walk-in closet and an updated en suite. The generous walk-out basement provides endless possibilities for expansion, with a convenient half bath. The property sits on over half an acre with mature trees for privacy and includes a backyard basketball court. With new HVAC, roof, water heater, windows, doors, and garage door and pad, this home is move-in ready. No HOA adds to the freedom of making this meticulously updated residence your own. Conveniently located minutes from downtown Covington Square, enjoy easy access to shopping and dining. Don't miss the opportunity to call this well-appointed home yours!
